__base()[1/3] __base__gnu_debug __gnu_debug__base template<typename _Iterator >
_GLIBCXX_CONSTEXPR _Iterator __gnu_debug::__base (_Iterator __it)[inline]
Helper function to extract base iterator of random access safe iterator in order to reduce performance impact of debug mode. Limited to random access iterator because it is the only category for which it is possible to check for correct iterators order in the __valid_range function thanks to the < operator.
